# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# DealershipAI Environment Configuration
# See: dealershipai-master-manifest.json for full documentation
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔐 Clerk Authentication
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/sign-in
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/sign-up
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL=/onboarding
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL=/onboarding

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🗄️ Database & Caching
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=
DIRECT_URL=

# Supabase (Alternative to Postgres)
SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# Upstash Redis (Caching & Rate Limiting)
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
KV_URL=
REDIS_URL=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🗺️ Maps & Geolocation (for Hero component)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GMAPS_KEY=                                    # Google Maps API key for nearby-dealer route
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_KEY=                       # Mapbox for future map features
MAPBOX_STYLE_URL=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🤖 AI Services
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenAI (for GPT-4, embeddings)
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Anthropic Claude (optional)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Model overrides (optional)
AIM_GPT_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
PULSE_ENGINE_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
SCHEMA_ENGINE_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# DealershipAI GPT API
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.gpt.dealershipai.com
DAI_API_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_DAI_API_KEY=

# Schema Engine
SCHEMA_ENGINE_URL=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🚀 Deployment & Infrastructure
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Application URLs
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
DEPLOY_URL=https://dealershipai.com

# Vercel (for CI/CD)
VERCEL_TOKEN=
VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=
VERCEL_ORG_ID=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📊 Analytics & Monitoring
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=                            # Google Analytics 4
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=
VERCEL_ANALYTICS_ID=
POSTHOG_KEY=
POSTHOG_HOST=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔔 Notifications
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL=                            # For deployment notifications

# SendGrid (email notifications)
SENDGRID_API_KEY=
SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@dealershipai.com

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 💳 Payments
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔒 Security & Cron
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CRON_SECRET=                                  # Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🎯 Pulse Configuration
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PULSE_TASK_BATCH_SIZE=10
PULSE_RETRY_ATTEMPTS=3
PULSE_DEBUG=false

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 👤 Admin
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADMIN_EMAILS=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔧 Next.js
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📝 Notes
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this to .env.local for local development
# 2. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 3. Set production values in Vercel project settings
# 4. See: .env.production.example for production template
# 5. Reference: dealershipai-master-manifest.json
